<h3>Cloudiness and Radiation</h3>
<br><br>
In July it was generally less cloudy than normal (the average calculated from the climatological period 1982 to 2009) over Europe with largest anomalies over France and Spain. Over France, we also find the largest surplus of radiation whereas negative anomalies in radiation are clearly visible over southern Europe, the United Kingdom and over the northeastern part of Europe.
